ion etc), then we may define our classes like this:\n\n```kotlin\ndata class Database(val host: String, val port: Int, val user: String, val pass: String)\ndata class Server(val port: Int, val redirectUrl: String)\ndata class Config(val env: String, val database: Database, val server: Server)\n```\n\nFor our staging environment, we may create a YAML (or Json,\n--- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sksamuel/hoplite/master/docs/getting-started.md\nERR HTTP Error 404: Not Found\n--- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sksamuel/hoplite/master/docs/hoplite-core.md\nERR HTTP Error 404: Not Found\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1782555565001}}
